{"tid":1217514,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽到大陸人話陳小春同王祖藍都去左示威","createTime":"2019-06-13T13:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T13:45:41.000Z","uid":29500,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a09632d12bb9475faded9672e2005a41c009e6f6","tid":1217514,"uid":29500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:13:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，尋日去完郊遊，仲要比狗追，<br />\n今日身心疲累 放工就去左dup骨<br />\n咁就聽到幾個大陸技師同兩個廢中師奶講612<br />\n一開始都係話咩好暴力呀 之類<br />\n聽到我就黎忍唔住爆鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n突然 個大陸女人話<br />\n「剛才客人給我看 陳小春和王祖藍都去了遊行哩～」<br />\n其他人：蛤～！？<br />\n師奶：怎麼會～他們賺夠中国錢了！？<br />\n廢中師奶2: 都係大陸做左好耐喇 應該真係賺夠<br />\n<br />\n然後就不停討論佢地以後唔駛返大陸<br />\n笑到我仆街 邊個巴打咁識玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46cc21dd42f354a9d36b4b5c86cd7fa153dc3d4","tid":1217514,"uid":8171,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkfDQJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkfDQJb.png&h=19003e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12b31967eac3a4bdec83b3d7c26a1897f5b1722","tid":1217514,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c46cc21dd42f354a9d36b4b5c86cd7fa153dc3d4","tid":1217514,"uid":8171,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MkfDQJb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMkfDQJb.png&h=19003e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\